  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 20-80

          -  informed consent

          -  no other malignancies

          -  cT2N0-cT3N2 according to JGCA 2nd edition

          -  ASA score&lt;3

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  distant metastasis(P1 or M1) under laparoscopic exploration

          -  Conglomerated N2

          -  early gastric cancer in permanent pathologic report
      </textblock>
